ype ID here\">\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f42\u0f49\u0f72\u0f66\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cWe two\u201d<\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"189\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f41\u0fb1\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f5a\u0f7c\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cYou\u201d (plural)<\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"189\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f41\u0f7c\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f5a\u0f7c\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cThey\u201d<\/p> <\/td> <\/tr> <tr> <td width=\"189\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">\u00a0<\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"189\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f41\u0fb1\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f42\u0f49\u0f72\u0f66\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cYou two\u201d (H)<\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"189\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f41\u0f7c\u0f0b\u0f42\u0f49\u0f72\u0f66\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cThose two\u201d<\/p> <\/td> <\/tr> <tr> <td width=\"189\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">\u00a0<\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"189\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">\u00a0<\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"189\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f41\u0f7c\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f42\u0f49\u0f72\u0f66\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cThose two\u201d<\/p> <\/td> <\/tr> <\/tbody> <\/table><p>\u00a0<\/p>","title":""}]}